d data. This ensures that it remains intact and not tampered with during tr=
ansmission. We=E2=80=99ll set the GCM using <a href=3D"https://pkg.go.dev/c=
rypto/cipher">the crypto/cipher package</a>, by adding the following code b=
elow to the end of <code class=3D"code-markup">main()</code>:</p>

